<figureCitation box="[976,1092,1617,1638]" captionStart="FIGURES 11 – 14" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1301,1324]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,481,1277]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[151,1436,481,1280]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 11 – 14. Right embolium of macropterous (11) Diaphorocoris arunachalami n. sp., (12) Diaphorocoris dubreuili Montandon, (13) Diaphorocoris kiliyur n. sp., (14) Diaphorocoris punctatissimus (Kirby)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203252/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Figs. 11, 14</figureCitation>
